Interface Computer<T extends Config<U,T>,U extends Computer<T,U>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Class of Config instance used by Computer implementation.
    U - Class of Computer implementation used by Config instance.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChecksumComputer, CRCComputer

    Interface for checksum and CRC calculations.
